BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Polycystic Ovary Syndrome \(PCOS\) affects 1 in 10 women of reproductive age, yet many go) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (undiagnosed for years. This workbook provides comprehensive tools for managing PCOS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (through nutrition, exercise, and lifestyle modifications that address the root causes:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (insulin resistance and inflammation.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
