98 0 obj
<< /Length 2769 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: Can PCOS be cured?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (PCOS is a lifelong condition, but symptoms can be managed extremely well through) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (lifestyle. Many women achieve regular ovulation, clear skin, and healthy weight through) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (diet and exercise alone.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Can I get pregnant with PCOS?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Yes! PCOS is the most common cause of ovulatory infertility, but it is also the most) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (treatable. Lifestyle changes, supplements \(inositol\), and medical interventions can help) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.4 Td (most women conceive.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 532.6 Td (Q: Will losing weight cure my PCOS?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (Weight loss can dramatically improve symptoms \(even 5-10% body weight\), but PCOS is not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 502.6 Td (caused by weight. Lean PCOS exists. Focus on insulin sensitivity and inflammation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 488.6 Td (regardless of weight.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 460.8 Td (Q: Is keto good for PCOS?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (Low-carb approaches can help insulin resistance, but very strict keto can raise cortisol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (and stress the body. Moderate low-carb \(under 100g carbs\) with adequate fiber is often the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 416.8 Td (best approach.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 389.0 Td (Q: Why is my hair falling out?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (PCOS-related hair loss is usually from excess androgens. It can improve with anti-androgen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.0 Td (treatment, inositol, zinc, and addressing the root insulin resistance. Be patient - hair) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 345.0 Td (cycles are slow.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 317.2 Td (Q: Does PCOS get worse with age?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.2 Td (Without management, metabolic risks increase with age. However, many women find symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 287.2 Td (actually improve in their 30s-40s, especially with consistent lifestyle management.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 259.4 Td (Q: Should I avoid dairy with PCOS?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 243.4 Td (Dairy can spike insulin and may worsen acne for some women with PCOS. Try eliminating it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 229.4 Td (for 3 months and observe. If tolerated, fermented dairy \(yogurt\) is better than milk.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 201.6 Td (Q: How long until supplements help?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185.6 Td (Most PCOS supplements take 3-6 months to show full effects \(the time for a full follicular) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 171.6 Td (cycle\). Be consistent and patient. Inositol often shows results in 2-3 months.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
